 ## ⚙️ 配置文件详解

 ### 主配置文件 `config.yml`

 #### 时间同步配置
 ```yaml
 time:
   # 是否按现实公历日期切换节气
   use-gregorian-trigger: true

   # 是否同步现实时间（关闭原版昼夜循环）
   sync-real-time: false

   # 自动刷新间隔（秒）
   refresh-interval-seconds: 60

   # 四季开始日期
   season-start-dates:
     spring: "03-04"
     summer: "06-04"
     autumn: "09-04"
     winter: "12-04"

   # 游戏天数循环（关闭公历触发时）
   season-duration-days:
     spring: 24
     summer: 24
     autumn: 24
     winter: 24
 ```

 #### 世界配置
 ```yaml
 worlds:
   # 是否默认启用全部世界
   enable-all: false

   # 启用的世界列表
   allowed:
     - world

   # 禁用的世界列表
   denied:
     - world_nether
     - world_the_end
 ```

 #### 季节效果配置
 ```yaml
 season-effects:
   spring:
     uncovered-crop-growth-multiplier: 1.25
     rain-chance: 45
     thunder-chance: 6

   summer:
     uncovered-crop-growth-multiplier: 2.0
     rain-chance: 25
     thunder-chance: 12

   autumn:
     uncovered-crop-growth-multiplier: 1.0
     rain-chance: 30
     thunder-chance: 4

   winter:
     uncovered-crop-growth-multiplier: 1.0
     uncovered-crop-stop: true
     rain-chance: 10
     thunder-chance: 0
 ```

 #### 视觉特效配置
 ```yaml
 visual-effects:
   interval-ticks: 40
   search-radius: 12

   aurora:
     enable: true
     chance-percent: 40

   blizzard:
     enable: true
     snow-placement-chance: 20

   falling-leaves:
     enable: true

   autumn-leaf-color:
     enable: true
     radius: 10
     budget-per-player: 24

   spring-cherry-leaf:
     enable: true

   tree-snow:
     enable: true

   apple-drop:
     enable: true
     chance-percent: 8
 ```

 #### 冬冻春融配置
 ```yaml
 season-world-rules:
   water-cycle:
     enable: true
     interval-ticks: 40
     search-radius: 6
     winter-freeze-chance-percent: 35
     spring-melt-chance-percent: 60
     transition-melt-radius-chunks: 6
     transition-melt-budget-per-tick: 512
